OL,3,CConcerns raised over health service
OL,4,Ccash-back waiting list scheme
OL,6,FConcerns have been raised that a cash-
OL,7,Fback healthcare scheme being
OL,8,Fintroduced to tackle waiting lists
OL,9,Fcould widen health inequality.
OL,11,FOn Tuesday, Health Minister Mike
OL,12,FNesbitt announced a package of
OL,13,Finitiatives to address "appalling"
OL,14,Fwait times.
OL,16,FThe #10m scheme will allow people to
OL,17,Ftravel for healthcare and claim back
OL,18,Fthe money at a later date.
