OL,3,CConcerns raised over health service
OL,4,Ccash-back waiting list scheme
OL,6,FAddressing concerns, the minister said
OL,7,Fanother #205million was being spent on
OL,8,Fother initiatives to bring down
OL,9,Fwaiting lists for treatment in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland currently has the
OL,13,Fworst hospital waiting lists of any
OL,14,Farea in the UK.
OL,16,FHow will the scheme work?
OL,18,FThe scheme has been welcomed by the
OL,19,Fmajority of MLAs but concerns have
OL,20,Fraised in the Assembly that it could
OL,21,Fwiden health inequalities.
