OL,6,FDiane Dodds MLA said: "What about that
OL,7,Fperson on that waiting list for a very
OL,8,Flong time that can't get that money
OL,9,Fand won't be able to access the scheme.
OL,11,F"How is this bringing equality to the
OL,12,Fhealth service in Northern Ireland and
OL,13,Fwhat can we do about that?"
