OL,6,FLeader of the Opposition Matthew
OL,7,FO'Toole said: "In the long term can he
OL,8,Fset out his aspiration for when he
OL,9,Fbelieves we can minimise the
OL,10,Fassumption that has been created in
OL,11,Four health system that you have to go
OL,12,Fprivate in order to get elective care
OL,13,Fdone.
OL,15,F"Has he got an aspiration to move us
OL,16,Fback towards the principle of a
OL,17,Fpublicly funded healthcare system free
OL,18,Fat the point of access?"
OL,20,FMr Nesbitt said: "It is #10m out of a
OL,21,Fbudget of #215m for waiting lists.
