OL,4,Ccash-back waiting list scheme
OL,6,F"There is up to #205m for people who
OL,7,Fwill not qualify for whatever reason
OL,8,Ffor that waiting initiative.
OL,10,F"If you look at my postbox since I
OL,11,Ftook post eleven months ago, nearly
OL,12,Fevery MLA has written to me asking me
OL,13,Fto bring back the cross-border
OL,14,Finitiative.
OL,16,F"This is just a re-working of that
OL,17,Finitiative. You are going to have been
OL,18,Fon a (Health Service waiting list) for
OL,19,Fat least two years and we are going to
OL,20,Fexpand it beyond the Republic to all
OL,21,FEU countries.
