OL,4,Ccash-back waiting list scheme
OL,6,F"But there is an equity issue, because
OL,7,Fyou have to pay for the procedure up
OL,8,Ffront and when you are claiming it
OL,9,Fback, you are only going to get what
OL,10,Fit would have cost to do it in the
OL,11,Fsystem here in Northern Ireland.
OL,13,F"That means if you are having to
OL,14,Ftravel, having to book accommodation,
OL,15,Fif you need to take somebody with you
OL,16,F- a carer, a partner, a relative -
OL,17,Fthat is not covered by the scheme."
